parameters:
\N<Luna>Hehe, no matter how many times I see it, the ocean is
beautiful, isn't it~

\N<Taro>Yeah, you're right... I've been so preoccupied with paying
off debts that I hadn't even thought about how we're going
to live...

\N<Taro>Making Luna-chan go through such inconvenience... I'm really
failing as a boyfriend.

\N<Luna>I'm fine with it, as long as I can be with you, Taro-kun,
anywhere is good.

\N<Luna>Look, even now, we can see this vast and beautiful ocean
together...

\N<Luna>Hey hey, there seems to be something like a door over
there... It's strange since this area is just a beach...

\N<Luna>It's out of sight, maybe it's a hideout? Should we go check
it out?

\N<Taro>...Eh?! Just entering an unknown place all of a sudden... Is
it really okay!?

\N<Luna>There's no particular presence and no sounds... If there's a
monster, we can just get out quickly, right?

With a feeling of clutching at straws, Taro cautiously
entered through the door.
